### Upload PNG → PDF
POST http://localhost:8000/convert/png-to-pdf
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ../fixtures/sample.png
--boundary--

### Poll task status
GET http://localhost:8000/tasks/{{task_id}}

### Download result
GET http://localhost:8000/tasks/{{task_id}}/download
